      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even sleep anymore. i just keep looking at the news and every single thing is just... death. the oceans, the fires, the extinction. it feels like we are all just living in a slow motion car crash. what is even the point of trying to build a life or a future when the planet is literally dying? it feels so much more logical to just not be part of it.",
