      "content": "but it's not just \"fear\" though. it's actual data. the feedback loops are already happening. i'm not just being dramatic, i'm being realistic. everything i do, every single thing i do, just adds to the carbon footprint of a species that's already doomed. it feels like forced participation in a catastrophe. how can you say there's a \"path forward\" when the math doesn't add up?",
